Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.33,0:00:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guts!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince of we\NThe Unforgiven
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We seek an audience with you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We shall meet.\Nin that time. at that place.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are kinsmen.\Noh blessed King of Longing.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was seen in Chet this time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of evil do these\Nstrange occurrences portend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy See is dispatching\Na commission of inquiry to investigate
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So even the Holy See\Nis taking action
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have you\Ncollapsing on us
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rickert is back
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He found out where\Nthey're keeping Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be hasty
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's reached their limit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been running for a year
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all completely exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not like we can\Ntake action immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you have to rest
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Rickert followed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a nice move
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I must hand it to the highly touted\Nfemale commander
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Band of the Hawk
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But in any kind of battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the moment the leader's head\Nis taken
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is the moment the outcome\Nis decided
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No ordinary foe, that's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I win
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell your men to put down\Ntheir swords and you'll live
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise,\NI'll cut your head off right now
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now choose on the count of three
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Two
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let this street performer\Ntire you out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together Commander
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! You came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Stop sitting around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of this
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You go and do your job
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back and don't interfere
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's mine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This blade of thunder\Nwill strike you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Silat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall back for now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it happened the day\Nafter you left
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, we're hailed as\Nthe saviors of Midland
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and in a single night,\Nwe're branded criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So much for becoming a noble
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess you couldn't\Ncare less about that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not accepting you back
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not some bastard who wasn't here\Nwhen he was needed most
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not my comrade
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.07,0:12:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,On guard
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You totally tried to kill me just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Casca!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look down on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Draw your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're reckless as ever
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You ruined everything
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith and the Band of the Hawk
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You destroyed it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How stupid are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one Griffith wanted\Nwas you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the only one\Nclose to Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You made Griffith weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith's
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,no good without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about Griffith here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! You're bleeding
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I just did my own thing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I get it!\NLet go, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to\Nbecome Griffith's sword
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,or his woman
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized long ago that there was\Nno place for me in his heart
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I refused to give up\Nbecause if I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You do the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! What the hell\Nwere you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! Never go near a cliff,\Never again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't deal with being dragged\Nalong again another time! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You took everything from me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like killing you right now
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always getting hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,because of me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always bleeding
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving after\Nwe rescue Griffith?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah I stick to my decisions
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You should come with me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me after\Nwe rescue Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:19:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what the future holds
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get enough of you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to have you\Nhundreds
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,thousands of times from here on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit calling me a fool
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware of that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Casca
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Casca!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I see the wheel has begun to turn
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I'm positive\Nhe was behind me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.49,0:22:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Heed my words, you who struggle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.86,0:22:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shortly, a rain of terror,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the likes of which\Nyou cannot control,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,shall descend upon you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.06,0:22:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A storm of death
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But take heart, you who struggle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.67,0:23:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist, challenge,\Nand struggle more
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.54,0:23:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That alone is the sword that\Nconfronts death
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.95,0:23:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not forget these words
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.35,0:23:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that all about?! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.50,0:23:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you find this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.86,0:23:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I had some help from the inside
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.27,0:24:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It means we're not the only ones\Nwho want to rescue Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.38,0:24:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But insiders from the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.55,0:24:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you with the Band of the Hawk?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.69,0:24:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've waited for you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.19,0:24:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You really did come
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.96,0:24:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.33,0:24:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the help from the inside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.83,0:24:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.75,0:24:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How far down does this hole go?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.95,0:24:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Many years ago\Nabout a thousand years
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.99,0:24:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,During the age of wars
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.72,0:24:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.76,0:25:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone appeared\Nwho put an end to the warring age
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.67,0:25:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Supreme King Gaiseric
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.03,0:25:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He conquered all the regions\Nof the continent
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.37,0:25:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and built an empire in\None generation
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.31,0:25:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's much mystery\Nsurrounding him
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.41,0:25:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was skilled in battle and
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.41,0:25:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it's said that he always wore\Na skull mask on the battlefield
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.55,0:25:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard the story of\Nthe Skull King before
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.05,0:25:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But the King became\Ndrunk with power,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.16,0:25:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and God sent five angels after him\Nand destroyed his capital
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.40,0:25:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it four?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.56,0:25:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So what does that fairy tale\Nhave to do with this hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.17,0:25:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a fairy tale!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.40,0:25:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,At least The capital did really exist
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.14,0:25:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Deep down at the bottom\Nof this tunnel
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.18,0:25:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.63,0:26:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.86,0:26:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.66,0:26:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.97,0:26:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gri-
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.57,0:26:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Grif fith?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.35,0:26:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.78,0:27:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The tendons in his arms and legs\Nhave been cut
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.66,0:27:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,His tongue too
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.59,0:27:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca! The key!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.63,0:27:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.87,0:27:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.11,0:27:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.08,0:27:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.08,0:27:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.07,0:28:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't escape now
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.07,0:28:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I just locked the door
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.14,0:28:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.31,0:28:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do this to Griffith?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.72,0:28:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never laid a hand on\Nsomeone so handsome
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.69,0:28:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was torture,\Nbut how can I put it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.93,0:28:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It gave me such a lift
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.63,0:28:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I cut the tendons\Nin his arms and legs,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.10,0:28:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so that he wouldn't try to escape
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.90,0:29:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then whenever he wasn't\Neating or sleeping,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.53,0:29:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I peeled off his skin,\Npulled out his nails,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.70,0:29:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,put hot irons on him,\Nput boiling water on him
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.78,0:29:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, we've been inseparable like\Nhusband and wife this past year
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.02,0:29:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Take at look at the best part\Nof my collection!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.92,0:29:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my lucky charm
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.79,0:29:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his tongue
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.60,0:29:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna die now
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.24,0:29:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go to heaven\Ndouble-tongued
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.74,0:29:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.98,0:29:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it\NYour breath reeks too badly
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.72,0:29:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.12,0:29:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hewup
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.99,0:29:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't hear you Speak clearly
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.07,0:30:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.23,0:30:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now drop your weapons\Nand surrender quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.04,0:30:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts, maybe we\Nshould retreat for now
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.85,0:30:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.13,0:30:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.17,0:30:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Shoot!\N- Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.98,0:30:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall behind Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.55,0:30:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.55,0:30:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith was taken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.25,0:31:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.49,0:31:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.19,0:31:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only a few of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.86,0:31:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Casca!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.83,0:31:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.74,0:31:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.54,0:31:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm honored to be able to assist\Nour kingdom's heroes
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.40,0:31:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Close the gates!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.96,0:31:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.83,0:31:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not let the rebels through!\NUnderstand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.31,0:31:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim for the horses! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.18,0:32:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The fools
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.28,0:32:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they intend to\Nforce their way out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.79,0:32:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, you fools?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.66,0:32:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.81,0:32:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.42,0:32:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we meet again
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.15,0:32:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.73,0:32:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the regular army
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.60,0:32:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,About fifty
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.70,0:32:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, a hundred!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.24,0:33:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.91,0:33:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't they approaching?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.88,0:33:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an ambush
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.59,0:33:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, behind us too!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.63,0:33:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys, take the front
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.86,0:33:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts, Pippin Cover the rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.21,0:33:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They are heinous criminals who\Ndare aim their arrows at the king
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.91,0:33:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.61,0:34:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The horse is hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.27,0:34:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't hold up much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.95,0:34:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, there's no end to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.75,0:34:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.29,0:34:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He made it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.86,0:34:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Corkus!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.66,0:34:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to do this
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.27,0:34:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.60,0:34:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.54,0:34:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, forget that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.42,0:35:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Cheers!\N- Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.96,0:35:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as Griffith is back,\Nvictory is ours
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.13,0:35:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Band of the Hawk is\Ncompletely revived
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.43,0:35:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah We'll win, and win\Nand keep on winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.54,0:35:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We should get a commission\Nwith Chuder
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.17,0:35:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll shock\Nthose Midland bastards
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.58,0:35:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.55,0:35:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'll get someone to\Nrelieve you right away
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.75,0:35:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right\NPlease rest, Commander
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.02,0:35:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't taken a break at all
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.22,0:35:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you guys to\Nworry about me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.34,0:35:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Griffith?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.01,0:35:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a doctor,\Nso I can't really
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.68,0:35:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.88,0:35:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.92,0:36:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that awfully hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.96,0:36:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take it off\NIt's just the two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.70,0:36:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You want that on?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.54,0:36:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just like you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.68,0:36:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed\NA year's passed
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.15,0:36:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this is still a war zone
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.65,0:36:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta have armor on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.09,0:36:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And they cut the tendons\Non his arms and legs
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.13,0:36:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't stand or\Nswing a sword
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.41,0:36:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.03,0:37:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Judeau told me
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.66,0:37:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.77,0:37:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.82,0:37:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, it's a joke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.05,0:37:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,About Griffith?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.72,0:37:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine I'll just ask him myself
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.49,0:37:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.39,0:37:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith can't speak anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.17,0:38:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.24,0:38:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't we gonna\Nstart all over again?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.38,0:38:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Griffith is back?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.15,0:38:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They labeled us criminals\Nfor no reason at all
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.69,0:38:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And for a year,\Nwe've been on the run
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.76,0:38:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost so many comrades\NAnd yet
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.33,0:38:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We kept our hopes up that\Nwhen Griffith returned
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.94,0:38:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.32,0:38:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.99,0:38:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.56,0:38:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.23,0:38:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Casca
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.56,0:38:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Band of the Hawk\Nain't dead yet
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.13,0:39:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If Commander Casca continues
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.37,0:39:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me some time
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.50,0:39:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be some time\Nuntil the next enemy attack
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.71,0:39:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me think it over until then
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.88,0:39:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.32,0:39:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you need to think over?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.12,0:39:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you about to\Ntell everyone just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.46,0:39:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.89,0:39:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That you have to finish\Nthe battles that you start
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.83,0:39:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so strong
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.63,0:39:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Because one chooses to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.17,0:39:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,one can't back out
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.64,0:39:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you say those same words\Nto Griffith?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.38,0:39:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all weak
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.48,0:39:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we rely on\Npeople and dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.79,0:39:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And is there anything we can do for\Nsomeone who's lost what they rely on?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.76,0:40:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we be kind? Or strict?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.66,0:40:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we stay by their side?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.43,0:40:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I wanted someone to\Nstay by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.57,0:40:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.67,0:40:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.21,0:40:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know either
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.82,0:40:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go see Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.93,0:40:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith I'm going to change\Nyour bandages
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.53,0:40:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what're you gonna do from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.10,0:40:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Set out on your travels again?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.61,0:40:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Judeau?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.88,0:40:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.61,0:40:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll recruit\Nthe guys who stay
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.45,0:40:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and form a band of thieves
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.85,0:41:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then at least,\Nwe can look after Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.09,0:41:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll join you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.69,0:41:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You already left us
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.26,0:41:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time, take Casca with you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.03,0:41:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.36,0:41:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to take her this time\NOr else
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.73,0:41:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.64,0:41:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.07,0:41:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.54,0:41:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Captain\N- Captain
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.34,0:41:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna disappear without\Na word again like the last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.71,0:41:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are,\Nplease take us with you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.78,0:41:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We decided together as raiders
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.22,0:41:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We've still got a lot left in us
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.45,0:41:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As mercenaries, or whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.99,0:41:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As long we have you, Captain
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.89,0:41:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- Captain\N- Hey, guys
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.03,0:41:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Please, Captain!\N- Captain
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.16,0:41:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all like family, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.93,0:41:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're wanted criminals\Nwherever we go,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.63,0:41:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,let's stick together!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.77,0:41:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're with us,\Nwe can manage!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.14,0:41:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Captain? Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.14,0:41:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Captain\N- Captain
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.11,0:42:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Captain\N- Captain
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.91,0:42:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Please, Captain!\N- Captain
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.20,0:42:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rickert is scouting ahead and
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.27,0:42:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,looking for roads to take us\Nacross the border
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.64,0:42:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows some people\Nin the Caronia Mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.83,0:42:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How strange This is
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.84,0:43:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I had the hang of it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.84,0:43:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so hopeless
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.75,0:43:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.45,0:43:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.35,0:43:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get another blanket
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.09,0:43:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.36,0:43:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Griffith?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.49,0:43:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Grif
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.56,0:43:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.80,0:43:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.88,0:44:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.85,0:44:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.73,0:44:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How's Griffith?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.89,0:44:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah He just went to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.23,0:44:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.83,0:44:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.10,0:44:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what is it? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.07,0:44:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.81,0:44:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.94,0:44:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.38,0:44:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen with Griffith?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.78,0:44:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.91,0:44:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.99,0:44:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.99,0:44:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I can't go
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.19,0:45:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.40,0:45:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go with you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.40,0:45:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith is so thin
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.70,0:45:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lost so much weight\Nhe's constantly shivering
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.27,0:45:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith who was\Nso proud and mighty
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.68,0:45:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave him
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.85,0:45:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the way he is now
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.45,0:45:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave him
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.69,0:45:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.00,0:45:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm staying too
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.14,0:45:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm staying with\Nthe Band of the Hawk
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.89,0:46:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what happened\Nat Promrose Hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.77,0:46:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.84,0:46:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you have to go
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.94,0:46:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are Griffith's equal
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.95,0:46:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are his friend
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.38,0:46:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You must go, even if it's alone
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.36,0:47:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you doing here?\NWhy are you so scared?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.76,0:47:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go. we're not done playing!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.33,0:47:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sun still hasn't gone down!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.94,0:48:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Griffith!\N- Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.34,0:48:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is the horse running wild?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.08,0:48:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think Griffith\Nheard us just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.45,0:48:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous\NHe can barely crawl
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.89,0:48:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Judeau and the others know!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.59,0:48:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.26,0:48:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lend me your horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.19,0:48:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.00,0:48:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.05,0:48:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.99,0:48:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I rested a bit too long.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.82,0:48:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got to go.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.19,0:48:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not done playing.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.33,0:48:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cobblestone path\Nin the back alley{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.90,0:49:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Continues on{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.87,0:51:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.97,0:51:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey look
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.11,0:52:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.59,0:52:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.27,0:52:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stay away!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.31,0:52:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stay away!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.62,0:52:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.93,0:52:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you touch me now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.07,0:53:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll never{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.39,0:53:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}never again with you!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.36,0:53:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.27,0:54:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.37,0:54:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.28,0:54:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.85,0:54:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.05,0:54:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.59,0:54:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd they come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.82,0:54:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Weren't we just crossing\Nthe grassland?! Right? Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.66,0:54:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.36,0:54:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch your step!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.53,0:54:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How could this be real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.70,0:54:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.84,0:54:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.54,0:54:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.94,0:54:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to rationalize something\Nyou don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.97,0:54:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.71,0:54:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Form a tight formation,\Ntake defensive positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.21,0:54:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're attacked now,\Nwe're all dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.88,0:54:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Judeau! Corkus!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.31,0:54:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaston! Pippin!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.45,0:54:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do a count,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.52,0:54:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- She's amazing\N- then keep your positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.75,0:54:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Arm those with crossbows!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.52,0:54:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stat!\N- Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.59,0:54:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.53,0:55:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Behelit?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.24,0:55:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.08,0:55:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.01,0:55:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.78,0:55:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.52,0:55:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come for\Nthe Great Nocturnal Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.88,0:55:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The feast that happens\Nonce every 216 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.79,0:55:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The eclipse!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.29,0:55:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eclipse?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.39,0:55:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.96,0:55:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,W-When'd they appear?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.46,0:55:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.63,0:55:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.87,0:55:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.67,0:55:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They are coming
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.00,0:55:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.37,0:55:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.47,0:55:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Our masters The sovereign\Nof the supreme beings!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.05,0:55:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The advent of\Nthe Four Guardian Angels!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.19,0:56:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lady Slan! Rejoice!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.39,0:56:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Slan!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.83,0:57:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.27,0:57:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.14,0:57:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gods
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.27,0:58:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.04,0:58:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.88,0:58:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ye lambs of the ungodly god\Nborn of man
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.68,0:58:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy this sacred\Nnocturnal festival to the fullest
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.06,0:58:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hawk
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.09,0:58:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,honorable child consecrated\Nby the laws of causality
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.36,0:58:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thou art the chosen one
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.23,0:58:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time, in this place
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.27,0:58:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The one chosen by\Nthe hand of the great god
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.14,0:58:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We art kinsmen\NO blessed King of Longing
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.85,0:58:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's one of them? Griffith?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.35,0:58:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.86,0:58:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't joke around
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.79,0:58:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.86,0:58:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.90,0:59:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Consecrated child? Kinsmen?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.93,0:59:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.80,0:59:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen this guy naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.84,0:59:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And one thing for sure,\Nhe ain't got a tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.61,0:59:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Such beautiful friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.75,0:59:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall make for\Nan excellent sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.82,0:59:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.86,0:59:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes A suitable sacrifice so\Nthat he may become a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.19,0:59:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment you took\Nthe Crimson Behelit in your hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.43,0:59:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you earned the right to\Nbecome a demon god
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.24,0:59:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the Egg of the King
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.67,0:59:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It enables one to be reborn\Nas one of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.31,0:59:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the Guardian Angels, the Godhand
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.78,0:59:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are all invaluable\Nsacrifices for the Angelic Advent
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.09,1:00:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dream, after all
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.44,1:00:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards You're gonna\Nchange Griffith into a monster?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.57,1:00:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange for our lives?!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.64,1:00:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not quite
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.31,1:00:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be of his own will
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.95,1:00:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He will offer you all\Nas sacrifices
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.97,1:00:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.94,1:00:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.21,1:00:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All lies within\Nthe currents of causality
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.34,1:00:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time\Nfor the Invocation of Doom
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.68,1:00:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Invocation of Doom!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.12,1:01:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the child to the altar!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.76,1:01:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts, Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.99,1:02:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you afraid?\NOne such as yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.03,1:02:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Of extraordinary beings\Nsuch as us?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.20,1:02:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps of the future\Nthat you will follow?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.44,1:02:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we enter the future
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.21,1:02:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's return once to\Nthe foundation of your past
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.57,1:03:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My. my{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.38,1:03:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such a noisy boy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.85,1:03:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's all this racket?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.78,1:03:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But old woman{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.08,1:03:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are so many dead people!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.92,1:03:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is all your doing.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.73,1:04:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of this{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.70,1:04:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you had never said that\Nyou were going to that castle{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.20,1:04:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}no one would have died!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.21,1:04:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.71,1:04:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't force anyone\Nto come with me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.18,1:04:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Silence!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.55,1:04:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You should have known.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.05,1:04:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You knew what kind\Nof place this is.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.06,1:04:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.46,1:04:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.49,1:04:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The only way to get to that castle\Nis to step over all these corpses.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.33,1:04:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otherwise. you will simply turn\Ninto a corpse as well!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.84,1:04:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... I...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.78,1:04:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Foolish boy!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.85,1:04:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you were going to have regrets.\Nyou should never have wished it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.49,1:04:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why couldn't you be satisfied{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.66,1:05:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with gazing at the castle\Nfrom the alleys?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.10,1:05:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.40,1:05:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.74,1:05:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.14,1:05:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I cannot say I'm sorry.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.54,1:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. I will not.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.58,1:05:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I apologize{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.55,1:05:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I regret it'll all be over.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.29,1:05:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll never get to reach that place.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.94,1:05:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.17,1:05:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That is you!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.21,1:05:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was an illusion?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.85,1:05:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't an illusion
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.32,1:05:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the reality\Nwithin your conscious realm
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.88,1:06:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.59,1:06:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyeing the castle in the heavens
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.12,1:06:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking it by piling up\Ncorpses endlessly
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.96,1:06:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That is you
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.27,1:06:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.00,1:06:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, your back alley path\Nhas been closed
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.21,1:06:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But behold
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.81,1:06:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who have flown with you
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.24,1:06:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Band of the Hawk
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.21,1:06:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Reeking of blood
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.22,1:06:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones left to you\Nuntil the very end of the road
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.69,1:06:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, you will be able\Nto keep on living
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.73,1:06:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Buried under the ruins\Nof your dream
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.20,1:06:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ruins of my dream?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.04,1:06:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pile them up
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.41,1:06:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All that has been left to you
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.64,1:07:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Chant the words "I sacrifice"\Nin your heart
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.72,1:07:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And you shall be granted\Nraven-black wings
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.69,1:07:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,upon which you shall soar\Nto the heavens
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.20,1:07:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.92,1:07:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.22,1:07:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Among the thousands.\Nthe tens of thousands of friend and foe{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.56,1:07:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are the only one\Nwho made me forget my dream.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.51,1:08:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sacrifice{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.65,1:08:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.46,1:08:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.77,1:08:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The threads bundled by the laws\Nof causality have now been bound
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.81,1:08:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The promised time has come
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.44,1:09:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.26,1:09:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been engraved\Nwith the brand of sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.60,1:09:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The lives of those engraved,\Nto the last drop of blood
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.40,1:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To the moment of agonizing death,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.34,1:09:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,will become sustenance for\Nthe new child of darkness
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.38,1:09:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Pippin!\N- Run!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.58,1:09:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Run! Run away\NYou must survive!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.49,1:09:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.22,1:10:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Judeau?!\NLet me go! Pippin is!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.17,1:10:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Pippin!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.34,1:10:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Judeau, turn back!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.58,1:10:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just let him die!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.08,1:10:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.75,1:10:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You are our general now
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.98,1:10:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You must survive this
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.82,1:10:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as the general lives,\Nthe Band of the Hawk lives!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.49,1:10:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As if As if we'll die like this!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.76,1:10:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the absolute end
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.33,1:10:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll struggle and fight,\Nand keep fighting our way through!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.96,1:11:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the rendezvous point
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.06,1:11:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you appeared, after all
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.13,1:11:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you've been our foe\Nfor a thousand years
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.93,1:11:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you wouldn't miss\Nthis opportunity
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.87,1:11:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were given the command\Nto guard the gate
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.51,1:11:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Immortal one
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.04,1:11:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like merrymaking
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.01,1:12:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know, my old friend
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.81,1:12:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a dream
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.11,1:12:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be a dream
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.42,1:12:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a bad dream
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.75,1:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just drunk at the usual pub
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.92,1:12:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone\NHurry up and wake me
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.29,1:12:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Judeau Pippin Rickert
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.43,1:12:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're there, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.37,1:12:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.58,1:13:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman in hell?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.49,1:13:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do me a favor\NDon't wake me up now
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.63,1:13:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.06,1:13:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it that a guy like me?\NDamn it!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.01,1:13:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.54,1:13:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you out of there real soon!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.88,1:13:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.58,1:13:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Save him?\NThere will be no such thing
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.19,1:13:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is his wish
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.22,1:13:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard it too
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.19,1:13:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He definitely
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.13,1:13:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.30,1:13:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd never say it!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.63,1:14:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd never!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.93,1:14:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Griffith is my
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.27,1:14:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.65,1:14:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Judeau!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.62,1:14:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! Move! You're gonna!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.16,1:14:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.43,1:14:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.88,1:14:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I get him with my knife?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.08,1:14:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you got him
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.08,1:14:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.49,1:14:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.42,1:14:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You just said we'll keep struggling\Nuntil the end!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.79,1:15:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand by your words
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.39,1:15:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, on your feet!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.56,1:15:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike Guts, I'm kinda fragile
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.07,1:15:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get wise and shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.07,1:15:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I'm good at
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.94,1:15:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- If you have time to move your mouth\N{\i1}- Yeah{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.34,1:15:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- I always thought I was{\i}\N- Move your legs! If you can't walk
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.41,1:15:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- more of a smooth talker than this{\i}\N- I'll carry you if I have to!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.20,1:15:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Judeau
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.37,1:15:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.78,1:17:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where am I?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.05,1:17:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All their deaths are piercing through me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.49,1:17:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's strange{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.59,1:17:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't feel a thing.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.41,1:17:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mind is overflowing with memories.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.77,1:17:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.07,1:18:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do people?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.14,1:18:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.48,1:18:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.25,1:19:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anyone left
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.02,1:19:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,alive?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.18,1:19:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone?!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.52,1:19:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.46,1:19:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Judeau!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.79,1:20:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Pippin! Corkus!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.93,1:20:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Raiders!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.13,1:20:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.45,1:20:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaston
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.26,1:20:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pippin!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.07,1:20:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pippin! You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.04,1:20:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pippin!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.47,1:21:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.71,1:21:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.02,1:21:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The birth
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.42,1:21:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fifth Blessed King
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.52,1:21:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The New Demon King!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.62,1:21:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Our new kinsman\Nto wear the mantle of evil
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.26,1:21:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wings of Darkness\NFemto!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.59,1:22:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Grif
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.31,1:23:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.95,1:23:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!\NWhat the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.87,1:24:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Grif fith?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.50,1:25:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool What can a mere human do?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.98,1:25:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He is an existence that\Nhas transcended humanity
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.76,1:26:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't look
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.29,1:26:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Such beauty
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.23,1:26:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes my breath away
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.53,1:26:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Love hatred
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.23,1:26:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain pleasure life death
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.53,1:26:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All are there
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.57,1:26:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is to be human
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.51,1:26:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is to be evil
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.42,1:28:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.06,1:28:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How unforeseen!
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.39,1:28:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot predict everything
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.26,1:29:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we are not gods
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.20,1:29:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But Void
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.34,1:29:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this also destined?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.99,1:29:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca?!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.03,1:29:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts?!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.23,1:29:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.30,1:29:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Time has already begun to flow
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.40,1:29:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The fifth angel has been born
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.74,1:29:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The time of darkness descends
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.68,1:29:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,An age when every darkness\Nshall eclipse light
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.85,1:29:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In time, man will call this
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.99,1:29:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Age of Darkness
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.09,1:30:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where're you all going?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.62,1:30:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Judeau!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.26,1:30:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.19,1:30:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.13,1:30:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Corkus! Pippin!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.24,1:30:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.57,1:30:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.74,1:30:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.65,1:31:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Guts! You're up
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.28,1:31:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rickert?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:36.39,1:31:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness\NI thought you wouldn't make it
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.19,1:31:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,For four days\NYou didn't move or blink
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.93,1:31:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.36,1:31:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The hills by my home
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.56,1:31:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is called Ore Cave
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.13,1:31:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened inside the tornado?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.71,1:31:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tornado?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.11,1:32:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Say
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.48,1:32:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Griffith's rescue?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.61,1:32:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you get hurt?\NWhat happened to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.65,1:32:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what happened!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.29,1:32:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca Where's Casca?!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.16,1:32:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Casca is Well
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.09,1:32:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca is over there
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.59,1:32:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.70,1:32:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me Guts
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.50,1:33:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.38,1:33:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Quit fooling around
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.78,1:33:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over Casca!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.32,1:33:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We got out of there\Nand survived!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.69,1:33:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Casca!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.26,1:33:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.23,1:33:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What a scary man, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.53,1:33:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Naughty, Guts
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.93,1:33:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bully Casca
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.01,1:33:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't remember
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.41,1:33:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you or me
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.58,1:33:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been like this\Nsince she woke up
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.12,1:33:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there It's all right
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.89,1:33:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know There's a good girl
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.40,1:34:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do I look funny?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.07,1:34:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn you! It's your fault!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.40,1:34:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Draw your sword!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.97,1:34:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fool{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.38,1:36:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.97,1:37:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.97,1:37:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.98,1:37:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Steel yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.41,1:37:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you will be devoured
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.42,1:37:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Brand of Sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.86,1:37:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,draws to it, those of darkness
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.03,1:37:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body and every drop of blood
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.80,1:38:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,has been given as an offering\Nto those of darkness
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.74,1:38:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the destiny of those
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.31,1:38:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,who receive the Brand of Sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.83,1:38:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Struggler indeed
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.88,1:38:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So it just means it's another battle
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.78,1:38:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's changed from before
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.32,1:38:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.63,1:39:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this time. take Casca with you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.97,1:39:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There he is. the bloodthirsty goon!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.87,1:39:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you are Griffith's equal{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.97,1:39:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you are his friend{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.91,1:39:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You must go. even if it's alone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.65,1:39:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is that crying?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.65,1:39:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.63,1:40:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tears?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.93,1:40:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The last that{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.67,1:40:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shed.{\i}

